name: topicmapping
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "topicmapping" %}
{% set version = "1.0.0" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  - url: https://bitbucket.org/andrealanci/{{ name }}/get/13bb57316ff0.zip
    fn: topicmapping.zip
    sha256: 765a1bb38ab164f1a56e7799a73bfe29ab6ec1d92f990cc38814e1c15eaf2b34
    patches:
      - "infomap.patch"
      - "infomap_path.patch"
  - path: Makefile

build:
  number: 0
  script: make
  include_recipe: False
  skip: True  # [win]

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ compiler('cxx') }}
    - make
    - libgomp  # [linux]
    - llvm-openmp  # [osx]
    
test:
  source_files:
    - quantum-and-granular-large-stemmed

about:
  home: https://bitbucket.org/andrealanci/topicmapping/src/master/
  summary: 'Topic Mapping algorithm implemented by Andrea Lancichinetti'
  license: GPL-3.0-or-later
  license_file: 
    - LICENSE
    - vendor/

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - TnTo
